@startuml
skinparam defaultFontName "Microsoft YaHei"
title 充电桩故障调度——时间顺序调度

actor "系统" as System
participant "SchedulingService" as SS
database "ChargingRequestRepository" as CRR
database "ChargingPileRepository" as CPR
database "SystemConfigRepository" as SCR

note over System: 充电桩故障触发 handlePileFault(pileId)

System -> SS: handlePileFault(pileId)
activate SS
SS -> CPR: findById(pileId)
CPR --> SS: ChargingPile (故障桩)
SS -> SS: pile.setWorkingState(FAULT)

SS -> CRR: findByPileIdAndCarStateAndActiveTrue(pileId, CHARGING)
CRR --> SS: List<ChargingRequest> (被中断的充电车辆)

loop for each interrupted car
    SS -> SS: request.setCarState(QUEUED)\nrequest.setPileId(null)
    SS -> SS: pile.occupiedSpots--
end
SS -> CPR: save(pile)

SS -> SCR: findAll() -> getConfig
SCR --> SS: SystemConfig (strategy=TIME_ORDER)

SS -> CRR: findByRequestModeAndCarStateAndActiveTrue\nOrderByRequestTimeAsc(mode, WAITING)
CRR --> SS: 等待车辆 (按申请时间升序)

loop for each waiting car (先来先分配)
    SS -> CPR: findByMode(mode) 找空闲桩\nfilter: (IDLE || CHARGING)\n&& occupiedSpots < parkingSpots\nmin(occupiedSpots)
    CPR --> SS: 最优空闲桩
    alt 有空闲桩
        SS -> SS: assignCarToPile(car, pile)\ncarState=QUEUED, 分配排队号
        SS -> CRR: save(car)
        SS -> CPR: save(pile)
    else 无空闲桩
        SS -> SS: break
    end
end

note over SS: 被中断车辆按申请时间重新分配
SS -> SS: redistributeFaultRecovery(interrupted, mode)\n按requestTime升序排序
loop for each interrupted (先申请先分配)
    SS -> SS: car.setCarState(WAITING)
    SS -> CRR: save(car)
    SS -> SS: dispatchWaitingCars(mode)
end

deactivate SS

@enduml
